      "text": [
        "1760 - وَ قَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «اَلْمَنُّ يَهْدِمُ اَلصَّنِيعَةَ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1760 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Reminding others of a favor destroys the good deed.\""
        ]
      }
